25|$|Bishop Robert de Limesey {{transferred}} his see to Coventry c. 1095, and in 1102 papal <b>authorisation</b> <b>for</b> {{this move}} also turned the monastery of St. Mary into a priory and cathedral. The subsequent rebuilding {{and expansion of}} St. Mary's was completed about 125 years later.|$|E
